{"tid":1251850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有勇武的支持，和平理性非暴力只是懦弱的包裝","createTime":"2019-06-22T17:03:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T08:04:59.000Z","uid":94457,"like":78,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e9ad4a9909ba489488d11754270f2fd54c32ab4f","tid":1251850,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:03:15.000Z","msg":"過去二十年，和理非路線毫無建樹<br />\n皆因和理非只是港人懼怕承擔抗爭後果的產物<br />\n甚麼爭取民意、階段性成果<br />\n在勇武派出現前都只是退縮的藉口<br />\n<br />\n而勇武派誕生，正正打破呢種困局<br />\n和理非不再是迫於無奈，而是一種選擇<br />\n當政府意識到港人有勇武的可能<br />\n港人先有機會憑和理非去撼動政權<br />\n<br />\n想繼續抗爭，一定一定要有勇武派<br />\n保護勇武派，應當是和理非首要的任務<br />\n既然今日有人願意為香港賭上一切<br />\n各位係咪都應該盡全力救返佢地出黎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請全力爭取特赦義士</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個義士都不能少</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e69c97800d704f9fbb0c7dfcfbc701ec2417082","tid":1251850,"uid":94457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:05:06.000Z","msg":"希望各位認清勇武派既重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個都不能少！"},{"pid":"2a9d26d25b92a79329af66a9a7ebe12ddbba7e36","tid":1251850,"uid":98726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:05:39.000Z","msg":"好話難聽，但講得好啱。推。"},{"pid":"7534c2f58d892fc177c8c2d70279c1e609b60761","tid":1251850,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:07:07.000Z","msg":"講得好"},{"pid":"c64d8cd93ebacd323aac15b754c23c59cd400805","tid":1251850,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:07:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b38798728056e1f8fc0bf96868f9b130a5b8e7a0","tid":1251850,"uid":94457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"每晚諗起被捕既義士<br />\n我都會覺得自己欠左佢地<br />\n所以我一定唔會放棄每一位義士<br />\n希望大家都可以將呢種諗法傳播俾身邊既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc91a075d8bb8b014fab33345e26074a31abcce","tid":1251850,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5e73bf1f21b83414ed64c33d077e7a2367da89a","tid":1251850,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:16:24.000Z","msg":"如果有朋友之後都會出黎<br />\n記得喊多啲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">特赦</span>"},{"pid":"d14c6200ad211930019be87112528623ed099f8a","tid":1251850,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:17:19.000Z","msg":"唔好再放棄佢地<br />\n就算係普通襲擊都唔得<br />\n政治檢控可恥"},{"pid":"ae2e65aeec2fca962c64fd1337830b3c9459ba6f","tid":1251850,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f78961c976055014f7127c2fc9cfeee254bb3575","tid":1251850,"uid":234407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"連登終於有人話，義士先係重點！"},{"pid":"39a23e7112a35372f1adf6e7919a2083c8254467","tid":1251850,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:18:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0bec5157e74706b953a530947c7c8e114d421c","tid":1251850,"uid":265467,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"Sorry ,借位一用<br />\n<br />\n大家應該由問題根源去思考,與其一樣樣去反對政府D賣港政策,點解唔用真普選趕走曬班賣港賊,必須要令更多人知問題根源核心,個個支持真普選!!!<br />\n<br />\n一日無真普選,建制派,港共政權賣港賊一車車補上,要徹底趕走賣港賊,只有真普選!!!<br />\n<br />\n[請廣傳]香港只有真普選先可以趕走港共政府同建制派賣港賊!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1251736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1251736</a>"},{"pid":"3b89807fdbcd118089c63df26a62aa1eabe4123e","tid":1251850,"uid":259423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T17:20:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"674a87c1fb5e4469892eb8f109e01bc6b8b1a1e0","tid":1251850,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-